22
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:49,380
=Episode 15=

23
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:54,040
When you marry, don't pick a scholar.

24
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:56,800
He doesn't know martial arts,
so he can't protect you.

25
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:02,600
Oh, you can't marry someone
with a meager income either.

26
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,080
His Highness said

27
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:07,640
girls mustn't marry someone
who can't afford rouge,  face powder,

28
00:02:08,040 --> 00:02:09,680
clothes, and dresses.

29
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,120
What are those?

30
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,640
These are

31
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,680
the clothes I prepared for you.

32
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,280
For me?

33
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,320
Thank you.

34
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,480
Zhilan,

35
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,960
when you reach the south,

36
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,280
the Nanchuan Army will meet you.

37
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,800
After everything has settled down,

38
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,080
I'll come pick you up.

39
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:52,760
Okay.

40
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,560
The Nanchuan Army has rebelled,
kill on sight.

41
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:49,000
Chu Li, are you afraid?

42
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,000
Afraid?

43
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,920
What's there to be afraid of?

44
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,560
You know I'm never afraid to die,
Your Highness.

45
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,640
What a reckless man.

46
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,760
When you have someone you want to protect,

47
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,800
you'll know what fear is.

48
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,960
Are you stopping me, General Chu?

49
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,040
I'll escort you.

50
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:57,200
(Zhilan, I'm leaving Cheng to you.)

51
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,640
(Tianyu Gate)
You insolent man.

52
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:06,320
I will cut off your head today

53
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,960
and grind your bones into ashes

54
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:11,240
to appease Ruyu's spirit.

55
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:14,200
Swords are truly for those
who are all brawn and no brain.

56
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,480
Charge!

